{"tid":1177682,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"南韓足球隊腳踩支那獎盃撒尿　強國網友怒吼","createTime":"2019-05-30T01:42:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-30T02:41:45.000Z","uid":32511,"like":51,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"f5ebe11b2f52f6f3cbd8ba21b1e622ca9c614b61","tid":1177682,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T01:42:19.000Z","msg":"南韓國家足球青隊隊員，近日參加中國舉辦的熊貓盃邀請賽並奪下冠軍，不過他們被拍到有隊員在頒獎典禮上，直接腳踩冠軍獎盃，甚至做出撒尿的動作，惹怒一大批中國網友，最後韓國球隊出面道歉。<br />\n<br />\n據中國《新浪網》報導，這支南韓球隊被拍到，在頒獎典禮上領獎後，又球員直接腳踩獎盃，甚至撒尿，其他球員還大笑。中國網友看到後，罵爆這群南韓球員：「和韓國人比賽，還不如人獸交。」、「自從出了勝利張紫妍案，對韓國男人真的感到噁心，再看這張圖，我真的要吐了。」、「恥辱啊。」、「這根本是把中國球員踩在腳下。」<br />\n<br />\n隨後熊貓盃主辦單位也立刻向南韓隊伍提出嚴正抗議和交涉，主辦單位也說：「歷屆熊貓盃的冠軍獎杯，都會放在所在國足協的足球博物館，組委會不清楚為何該隊員要侮辱屬於自己國家具有十分意義的獎盃。」<br />\n<br />\n最後南韓隊果然頂不住中國網友的壓力，韓國U18主帥金正秀出面道歉：「首先我要就事情的發生道歉，這完全是我的錯誤，我們希望兩國足協能維持友好關係，我們的球員不會再做出類似舉動，我們再次道歉，我們傷害了中國人的感情。」"},{"pid":"0581d1737878863b6ea195cb604b22ffab9abf5a","tid":1177682,"uid":35914,"like":15,"dislike":1,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T01:45:59.000Z","msg":"恥辱係踢咗咁多年都仲係咁垃圾，有本事咪贏返人地囉"},{"pid":"e0325779d9edf87f6a54d569a34e733fc9278504","tid":1177682,"uid":191762,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T01:47:39.000Z","msg":"韓國u18擺到明唔妥中國"},{"pid":"e5c95bdcb602f5fe4ad9b3ecd5025a5c2050d87f","tid":1177682,"uid":19126,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T01:48:43.000Z","msg":"狗咬狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20d4d8a58e10c9c1355182b9a3173cdc15919c5f","tid":1177682,"uid":191762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T01:49:51.000Z","msg":"屌你老母對韓國泰國紐西蘭一球都入唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"613d7c3defc436eff90b8b77e1cfc6ee99869096","tid":1177682,"uid":36134,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T01:50:52.000Z","msg":"道歉完背後繼續笑鳩支那<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而家全世界就係針對你支那 吹咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80a7870ad637001cee32ac835f1bfe823d26eeeb","tid":1177682,"uid":20473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0325779d9edf87f6a54d569a34e733fc9278504","tid":1177682,"uid":191762,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T01:47:39.000Z","msg":"韓國u18擺到明唔妥中國"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T01:51:43.000Z","msg":"冇乜邊個妥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b8b0ceef44bc067853b6da1dd348ce399b37229","tid":1177682,"uid":191762,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"80a7870ad637001cee32ac835f1bfe823d26eeeb","tid":1177682,"uid":20473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e0325779d9edf87f6a54d569a34e733fc9278504","tid":1177682,"uid":191762,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T01:47:39.000Z","msg":"韓國u18擺到明唔妥中國"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T01:51:43.000Z","msg":"冇乜邊個妥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T01:52:33.000Z","msg":"兜口兜面當垃圾真係未見過"},{"pid":"2ab9c7c3969c09c9e0aad5cb701d025fe0840300","tid":1177682,"uid":103207,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T01:52:38.000Z","msg":"南韓隊 : 狗也不屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53e2c17dc05d93990b172b0c38748597bbcb05d9","tid":1177682,"uid":6111,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T01:53:01.000Z","msg":"想問支那有冇贏過南韓？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c472e6ed87705d8320e9ee090a44ce929729de62","tid":1177682,"uid":54264,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-30T01:54:38.000Z","msg":"華為零件<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"207577b413f24e03a5342d04542ca86a297949a4","tid":1177682,"uid":2772,"like":3